Daniel Sturridge ya ceci Liverpool daga rashin nasara a Premier League a kan Chelsea ta hanyar zira kwallo a minti na 89 a ranar Asabar a Stamford Bridge, London.
Sturridge ya samu kwallon daga Xherdan Shaqiri ne a mita 30 daga burin Chelsea yayin da matsayi ya kasance 1-0.
Ya tura kwallon zuwa hagu kafin ya buga shi sama da zuwa ga manufa.
Gwajin ya tashi sama da filin wasa kuma ya fadi zuwa kusurwar dama ta sama na manufa.
