Rosa za ta koma arewa a ranar Lahadi.
A halin yanzu, ana samun wani yanayi na low pressure a kan Pacific Ocean wanda ke motsawa zuwa gabas zuwa gabar yammacin Amurka. Rosa ya kusanci Baja California a ranar Litinin a cikin wani hadari na wurare masu zafi, kuma zai motsa zafi na wurare masu zafi zuwa arewa zuwa kudu maso yammacin Amurka.
A ranar Litinin ne ruwan sama zai kai har inci 25 a wasu yankunan Mexico.
Rashin zafi na wurare masu zafi zai yi tasiri tare da ƙananan matsin lamba kuma ya haifar da ruwan sama mai yawa a kudu maso yammacin kwanakin nan.
A cikin gida, tsakanin 3 da 10 centimeters na ruwan sama na iya haifar da hadari da kuma yiwuwar landscreening a cikin hamada.
Yanayin zafi na wurare masu zafi zai haifar da ruwan sama tsakanin 5 da 7 centimeters a sa'a a wasu sassan kudu maso yammacin Amurka, musamman a sassan kudancin Nevada da Arizona.
Ana sa ran ruwan sama tsakanin 5 da 10 centimeters a wasu sassan kudu maso yammacin Amurka; musamman a kan manyan sassan Arizona.
Ruwa mai haɗari zai iya faruwa saboda yaduwar ƙasa da ruwan sama na wurare masu zafi.
An yi gargadin kada a yi tafiya a cikin hamada a ƙafa saboda haɗarin ruwan sama na wurare masu zafi.
Ruwan sama zai iya haifar da raguwa a cikin koguna masu gudana kuma walƙiya da hadari za su kawo iska mai ƙarfi da ƙura.
Ƙarƙashin matsin zai kuma kawo ruwan sama zuwa sassan gabar tekun kudancin California.
