A lokaci guda kuma, tattaunawar siyasa ta ci gaba, tare da katsewar shirye-shiryen talabijin na yau da kullum na kamfanonin watsa shirye-shirye daban-daban don bayyana abubuwan da suka faru a ranar Jumma'a: yarjejeniyar da aka cimma ta Arizona San Jeff Flake cewa FBI a cikin mako mai zuwa zai bincika zargin.
Ford ta shaidawa kwamitin cewa ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade lokacin da ya bugu kuma ya yi kokarin cire rigarta a wani bikin makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh ya ce, a lokacin sauraronsa, cewa yana da tabbacin cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila sama da mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli sauraron ranar Juma'a, a cewar Nielsen.
Kamfanin ya zo ga wannan adadi ta hanyar gano matsakaicin yawan masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News da MSNBC.
Ba a bayyana wannan labarin ba daga sauran tashoshin da suka nuna wannan sauraron, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen kuma yana da matsala wajen kirga masu kallo daga ofishin.
Don sanya wannan a cikin hangen nesa, akwai irin wannan adadin masu kallo da ke kallon wasan karshe na kwallon kafa ko kuma bikin karramawar Oscar.
Masu watsa labaran Fox News sun goyi bayan Kavanaugh, kuma tashar ita ce kuma ta fi yawan masu kallo a cikin rana tare da masu kallo miliyan 5,69, in ji Nielsen.
