An yi wa Erdogan maraba da bambanci a Köln
Shugabannin Turkiya da Jamus sun yi murmushi a karkashin sararin sama lokacin da suka hadu don cin karin kumallo a ranar Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba a Berlin.
Ranar karshe ce ta ziyarar Erdogan mai cike da cece-kuce a Jamus - wanda ake fatan zai gyara alakar NATO biyu.
Kasashen sun kasance masu rashin jituwa a kan hakkin dan adam, 'yancin latsa da kuma matsayin Turkiya a cikin EU.
Erdogan ya tafi Köln don bude babban masallaci.
Birnin yana da mafi yawan yawan jama'ar Turkiyya a waje da Turkiyya.
'Yan sanda sun hana taron mutane sama da 25 000 tattaruwarsu a gaban masallacin saboda dalilai na tsaro, amma da yawa daga cikin magoya bayan Erdogan sun taru don ganin shugaban.
Daruruwan masu zanga-zanga a kan Erdogan - da dama daga cikinsu Kurdawa - sun taru don yin tir da manufofin Erdogan da kuma shawarar da gwamnatin Jamus ta yanke na yi masa maraba a kasar.
Masu adawa da juna sun nuna bambanci tsakanin Turkawa na Jamus, wadanda suke kallon Erdogan a matsayin gwarzo, da kuma wasu, wadanda suke kallon shi a matsayin mai mulkin kai.
