Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya sha wahala sosai a lokacin da 'yan Democrat suka yi masa fushi
"Zaɓen da aka yi wa mai shari'a Kavanaugh ya zama ƙuri'a ne da aka yi wa rashin tausayi da kuma dabarun da ba su dace ba na 'yan Democrat", in ji Trump a wani taro a Wheeling, West-Virginia.
Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya sha wahala a lokacin da 'yan Democrat suka yi mummunan aiki a tsarin zaben.
Kavanaugh ya shaida a gaban majalisa a ranar Alhamis, yana musanta zargin da Christine Blasey Ford ya yi mata na cin zarafinta shekaru da dama da suka gabata, lokacin da suke matasa.
Ford kuma ya ba da shaida game da zargin da aka yi mata a lokacin sauraron.
Shugaban ya ce a ranar Asabar cewa jama'ar Amurka sun ga yadda Kavanaugh yake da ban mamaki da kuma karfin zuciya a wannan rana.
"Muryar Alkali Kavanaugh muryar daya daga cikin manyan lauyoyi na zamaninmu, lauya mai cikakken aiki a gwamnati", ya fada wa taron jama'a a West Virginia.
Shugaban ya kuma yi nuni da nadin Kavanaugh lokacin da yake magana game da muhimmancin kada kuri'a a zaben Amurka na jam'iyyar Republican.
Makonni biyar na daya daga cikin muhimman zaɓuɓɓuka a rayuwarmu.
Ba na yin addu'a, amma ina yin addu'a da gaske, "in ji shi.
