Tun da China na kara aiki a kan ilimin kere kere, Amurka ta kamata ta ninka jarinta a binciken da ake yi kan batun, in ji mai zuba jari kuma mai amfani da ilimin kere kere, Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Kalamansa sun zo ne bayan sassa daban-daban na gwamnatin Amurka sun bayyana kansu game da hankali na wucin gadi, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata hanyar da ta dace don amfani da hankali na wucin gadi.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirin ta a bara, kuma tana da burin zama ta farko a cikin kirkirar kere kere ta wucin gadi nan da shekarar 2030.
"Doubling of the budget for research on artificial intelligence zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, tun da duk sauran kasashe suna baya da Amurka, kuma muna neman ci gaba na gaba a artificial intelligence", Lee ya ce.
"Abin da ya fi wannan yawa shi ne, samun kudi mai yawa zai iya ninka yiwuwar samun babbar nasara a fannin fasaha ta wucin gadi a Amurka", Lee ya fada wa CNBC a cikin wata hira da ya yi da shi a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda ya wallafa littafinsa AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order a wannan watan ta hanyar kamfanin Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne shugaban zartarwa (CEO) na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin fasaha na kasar Sin, Face++.
A cikin shekarun 1980, ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon tare da tsarin fasaha wanda ya doke dan wasan da ya fi girma na wasan Othello, kuma daga bisani ya yi aiki a matsayin shugaban Microsoft Research kuma ya kasance shugaban Google a kasar Sin.
Lee ya amince da gasar fasaha da aka shirya a baya da gwamnatin Amurka, kamar Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency's Robotics Challenge kuma ya tambayi lokacin da gasar ta gaba za ta kasance, don haka ya kasance tare da gano masu hangen nesa na gaba.
"Masu bincike a Amurka yawanci suna aiki tukuru domin samun tallafin gwamnati", in ji Lee.
"Ba kasar Sin ce ke daukar shugabannin ilimi ba, manyan kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun yi hayar ɗaliban jami'a masu kyau don su yi aiki a kan ilimin kere kere na shekaru da dama da suka gabata.
Lee ya ce sauye-sauye a manufofin shige da fice na iya taimakawa Amurka wajen karfafa bincike kan ilimin kere kere.
"Ina ganin daliban digiri a fannin kere kere za su samu izinin zama a kai tsaye", in ji shi.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kasar Sin ta wallafa shirinta na samar da fasahar kere kere ta gaba a watan Yuli na shekarar 2017.
