Lokacin Taron Trump na Yammacin Virginia, YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara kamfen dinsa na neman zabe a wannan yammacin nan a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tasha biyar da Trump ya shirya a makon da ya gabata, ciki har da tasha a wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da aka samu kuri'ar tabbatar da zaben da zai cika mukamin da ya rage na Majalisar Dattijai, Trump ya yi niyyar gina goyon baya ga zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, tun da yake 'yan Republican suna cikin hatsarin rasa iko a kan majalisa a lokacin da za a ba da kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne Trump zai kasance a West Virginia yau da dare, kuma ta yaya za ku iya ganin sa a intanet?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia zuwa karfe 19:00 na yamma, Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya ganin jawabin Trump na yammacin Virginia a kan layi a kasa, ta hanyar watsa shirye-shirye ta YouTube.
Trump zai iya daukar sauraron zaben da aka yi a wannan makon na wanda aka nada a kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka zargi da laifin cin zarafin mata, tare da sa ran amincewar majalisar dattawa har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan taro shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su yi nasara a zaben watan Nuwamba kuma su sami wani abu mai karfi.
Kamfanin yakin neman zaben shugaba Trump ya ce wadannan tarurruka guda biyar da za su gudana a mako mai zuwa, na nufin tayar da hankalin masu sa kai da magoya bayan jam'iyyar Republican da suke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisa abu ne mai matukar muhimmanci a ajandarsa, don haka shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai iya a lokacin da muke shiga lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda ya ki bayyanawa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
An shirya taron ne a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, inda masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania za su halarci taron, kuma kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh za su dauki nauyin taron, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
Ranar Alhamis ce karo na biyu a cikin watan da ya gabata da Trump ya ziyarci jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe fiye da kashi 40 a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ake nema a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban kasa dole ne ya zo ya yi kokarin ba shi karin haske a zaben jama'a", in ji Simon Haeder, wani mai bincike kan harkokin siyasa a jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
