Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba zai yiwu a yi yaki da kai ba tare da amincewa ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa idan aka ci gaba da takunkumin, to rashin amincewar Amurka zai kara karuwa, kuma kasar ba za ta daina amfani da makaman nukiliya ba a wani yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaidawa taron shekara-shekara na gwamnatin duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki muhimman matakai domin inganta halin da take ciki a shekarar da ta gabata, misali ta dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da na missile, ta lalata wurin gwajin nukiliya, kuma ta yi alkawarin ba za ta yada makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya ba.
"Ba za mu samu wani abu mai kama da haka daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, babu amincewa da tsaron kasa, kuma a irin wannan yanayi, ba zai yiwu ba mu fara kawar da makamai".
Yayin da Ri, wani sanannen dan kasar Koriya ta Arewa, ya gabatar da korafi da dama kan kin amincewar Washington da tsarin kawar da makaman nukiliya, wanda zai biya Koriya ta Arewa albashi don daukar matakai na mataki-mataki, ya nuna rashin amincewarsa da cewa bai yi watsi da tsarin gina makaman nukiliya ba, kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni da wata sanarwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka fitar a taron farko da aka taba yi tsakanin shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki don hana gina makaman nukiliya a yankin Koriya ta Arewa, yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin samar da tabbacin tsaro ga Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta bukaci a kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce sai Pyongyang ta fara ba da makaman nukiliyarta.
Washington ta kuma yi adawa da tattaunawar sauƙaƙa takunkumin kasa da kasa a Koriya ta Arewa.
Amurka ta dage kan "saukar da makamashin nukiliya da farko" kuma ta kara matsa lamba da takunkumi don cimma manufar ta da karfi, kuma sun yi adawa har da a'idar dakatar da zaman lafiya, in ji Ri.
Imani da cewa takunkumi zai iya karya mu, fatan karya ne a tsakanin wadanda basu damu da mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, idan takunkumin ya ci gaba, to rashin amincewarmu zai kara.
Ri bai ambaci wani abu ba game da shirin sabon taron Kim da Trump, wanda shugaban Amurka ya yi a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon nan.
Maimakon haka ministan ya jaddada ganawa uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu, Moon Jae-in, a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kara da cewa: Idan bangaren wannan shirin na kawar da makaman nukiliya Koriya ta Kudu ce, ba Amurka ba, to, rashin gina yankin Koriya ba zai tsaya ba kamar yadda ya yi yanzu
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya sha bamban da na shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya shaida wa babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba zai yiwu a dakatar da makamai masu linzami na Koriya ta Arewa ba a kan Amurka, bayan da shugaban kasar Trump ya kira Kim a matsayin mai kai hari kan aikin kashe kansa.
Trump, wanda a shekarar da ta gabata ya yi imani da total annihila Koriya ta Arewa, ya yaba wa Kim saboda karfin gwiwar da ya nuna na daukar matakai don kawar da makamansa, amma ya ce har yanzu akwai aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da sanya takunkumi ga Koriya ta Arewa da ta kawar da makaman nukiliyarta.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da wani lokaci, ya ce, "Ko shekara biyu, uku ko watanni biyar, ba kome.
Sin da Rasha sun ce ya kamata Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta biya Pyongyang diyya saboda ayyukan da ta yi.
Amma sakataren harkokin wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya fadawa majalisar tsaro ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ranar Alhamis cewa: "Ya kamata a ci gaba da kiyaye takunkumin majalisar tsaro da karfi kuma ba tare da kasawa ba har sai mun samu cikakkiyar, karshe, tabbatar da kawar da makaman nukiliya".
Hukumar tsaro ta kasa ta amince da karin takunkumin da aka kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa tun 2006 saboda lalata shirin nukiliya da makamai masu linzami na Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a wajen taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, sannan ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe domin shirya wani sabon taron kolin.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma ziyararsa ta karshe ba ta yi kyau ba.
Ya bar birnin Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa an samu ci gaba, amma sa'o'i kadan bayan haka Koriya ta Arewa ta yi masa Allah wadai da cewa ya yi wa 'yan ta'adda irin wannan ikirarin.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin a wani taro da Moon a wannan watan cewa za ta lalata wani makami da kuma wani makami mai linzami idan Amurka ta dauki irin wannan matakin.
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa irin wannan matakin da yake nema, tabbacin tsaro ne kamar yadda Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore, kuma mataki ne na daidaita dangantakarsa da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna daukar darasi kan samun isasshen hutu
Wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekara ya yi amfani da shi wajen kara wa dalibai barci, a kokarin da yake yi na yaki da al'adun macho da ke kara girma da ke nuna cewa ana karatu cikin kafeyin duk dare.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa dalibai a manyan jami'o'i sau da yawa ba su da hankali game da ainihin abin da ya kamata su kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a fannin maganin barci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da Women, ya kirkiro wannan darasi, wanda ya yi imanin shine na farko a Amurka.
Ya samu wahayi ya fara wannan darasi bayan ya yi magana game da tasirin rashin barci akan ilmantarwa.
A ƙarshen, wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce, "Me ya sa ake gaya mini wannan yanzu da na tsufa?"
Ta ce babu wanda ya gaya mata muhimmancin barci, abin da ya ba ni mamaki, ya gaya wa The Telegraph.
Wannan darasi, wanda aka fara gabatar da shi a wannan shekara, ya bayyana wa dalibai muhimmancin yadda kyawawan halaye na barci ke taimakawa wajen samun nasara a harkokin ilimi da kuma wasanni, da kuma inganta lafiyarsu.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma manajan daraktan ayyukan kiwon lafiya na jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan darasi ne bayan daliban sun samu mummunar rashin bacci a cikin mako.
Wannan darasi na tsawon sa'a yana da nau'i na ayyuka masu ma'ana.
A cikin wani sashe akwai hoton ɗakin kwana, inda dalibai ke danna kofi, labule, masu horarwa da littattafai don a gaya musu game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda tasirin wasan motsa jiki ke shafar rashin barci, da kuma muhimmancin daren dare.
A wani sashe kuma an gaya wa mahalarta yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya kara hadarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, bakin ciki da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar makarantar, tare da gumakan hulɗa, yana ƙarfafa mahalarta suyi tunani game da ayyukan yau da kullum.
'Mun san ba zai canza halin nan take ba.
Amma muna ganin suna da hakkin su san -- kamar yadda kuke da hakkin ku san, tasirin lafiyar da zaɓin shan sigari ke haifarwa, "in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
"Abubuwan da suka faru a wannan lokacin sun nuna cewa rashin barci yana da matsala mai girma.
Tabbatar da samun isasshen, ingancin bacci, ya kamata ya zama makamin dalibi na sirri akan damuwa, gajiya da damuwa, ya ce - har ma da kaucewa samun nauyi, tunda rashin bacci yana sanya kwakwalwa cikin yanayin yunwa kuma yana sanya ku jin yunwa koyaushe.
Raymond So, dan shekara 19 daga California da ke nazarin kimiyyar halitta da kuma ilimin lissafi, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen samar da wannan darasi, bayan ya yi karatu a Harvard a shekararsa ta farko.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya bude masa idanu kuma ya karfafa masa gwiwa ya nemi a samar da darasi ga dukan jami'a.
Mataki na gaba, yana fata, shine a nemi dukkan daliban digiri su kammala irin wannan shirin kafin su shiga wannan babbar ma'aikata.
Farfesa Czeisler ya shawarci dalibai su yi la'akari da sanya ƙararrawa a lokacin da za su kwanta, da kuma lokacin da za su farka, kuma su san tasirin cutarwa na haske mai launin shuɗi wanda ke fitowa daga fuskokin lantarki da hasken LED, wanda zai iya canza sa'a na ciki gaba ɗaya, wanda ke haifar da matsalolin barci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: Menga-goal ya sa sojojin Gerrard su fadi
Rangers sun sake samun nasara a kan hanyar gudu lokacin da Dolly Menga ta aika da shafin Steven Gerrard zuwa ga asarar 1 0 a Livingston.
Ibrox sun yi fatan samun nasara ta farko a kan hanyar gudu tun bayan nasarar 4-1 da suka yi a St Johnstone a watan Fabrairu, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta yi nasara a karo na biyu a wasanni 18 da suka gabata, inda ta ci maki takwas, a zagaye na biyu a karkashin jagorancin Ladbroke na Premier League, Hearts.
Menga ya buga minti bakwai kafin rabin lokaci, kuma Ranger-uppstilling tare da rashin inspiration bai taba ganin zai daidaita ba.
Yayin da Rangers suka fadi zuwa matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa na uku kuma ya kasance kawai a baya Hibernian a kan bambancin raga.
Kuma akwai wasu matsaloli da zasu iya faruwa ga Rangers bayan da Calum Spence ya yi jinya saboda ciwon kai, bayan da aka jefa wani abu daga gefe.
Gerrard ya yi sauye-sauye takwas a tawagar da suka kai Ayr cikin wasan karshe na gasar cin kofin Betfred.
Holt, a gefe guda, ya tafi tare da Livy 11 wanda ya ɗauki maki tare da wani mafarki mai ban mamaki a makon da ya gabata, kuma zai yi farin ciki game da yadda abin da yake da shi ya ɗauki kisan gilla a kan abokan hamayyarsa a kowane lokaci.
Watakila Rangers sun fi kowa samun kwallon, amma Livingston ya fi yin wasa da kwallon da suke da shi.
Ya kamata su ci bayan minti biyu kawai lokacin da farko na Menga ya aika Scott Pittman zuwa Allan McGregor, amma dan wasan ya kasa a cikin babbar damarsa.
Wani dogon frispark daga Keaghan Jacobs ya sami kyaftin Craig Halkett, amma mai kare shi, Alan Lithgow, zai iya harba kawai a kan dawowa.
Rangers sun dauki iko, amma ya zama kamar akwai bege fiye da imani a wasan su a zagaye na uku.
Alfredo Morellos ya san cewa ya kamata ya yi hukunci a kan 20 mita lokacin da shi da Steven Lawless suka haɗu, amma alƙali Steven Thomson ya yi watsi da sha'awar dan wasan.
Rangers sun samu harbi biyu kawai a raga a farkon rabin, amma tsohon dan wasan Ibrox Liam Kelly ya damu da Lassana Coulibaly da kuma harbi mai kyau daga Ovie Ejaria.
Duk da yake Livi ya bude a minti na 34 watakila ya saba wa dokokin wasa, babu wanda zai iya musanta cewa sun yi hakan ne kawai saboda shotet.
Har yanzu Rangers sun kasa magance mummunan kisa daga Jacobs.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya buga kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya riƙe kansa don ya fitar da Menga don kammala mai sauƙi.
Gerrard ya bar hutu kamar dai ya canza Coulibaly tare da Ryan Kent kuma musayar ta haifar da sakamako na nan da nan lokacin da mai wasan ya yi wa Morelos wuri, amma Kelly mai ban sha'awa ya tsere don toshewa.
Amma Livingstone ya ci gaba da ƙididdigewa da baƙi don yin daidai da wasan da suke so, tare da Lithgow da Halkett aikawa da dogon lokaci a kan dogon lokaci.
Kungiyar Holt na iya kara jagorancinsa a karshen, amma McGregor ya yi nasara wajen hana Jacobs a cikin hakan, har sai Lithgrow ya sanya wani dogon zane daga alamar corner.
Mai tsaron Ranger, Glenn Middleton, yana da sabon buƙatar azabtarwa lokacin da yake goyon bayan tare da Jacobs, amma Thomson ya sake watsi da shi.
