Kasar Sin ta samu karuwar sabbin cututtuka da kashi 14 cikin dari
China ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suka kamu a kasar, in ji hukumar lafiya.
Kimanin sabbin abubuwa 40,000 ne aka ruwaito a cikin kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018.
Yawancin sababbin lokuta an kawo su ta hanyar jima'i, kuma sun nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance cutar HIV ta yadu cikin sauri ta wasu sassan kasar Sin sakamakon kamuwa da jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a Yunnan.
Duk da haka, a duk shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a kasar Sin ya karu da mutum 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
