Shi ma asali ya dogara ne akan matafiyi da kuma mutum mai ban mamaki na duniya Atkinson wanda aka buga a cikin tallan TV na Barclaycard da aka manta da shi, wanda ya bar rikici a baya.
Akwai wani kyakkyawan lokaci ko biyu a wannan tafiya ta ƙarshe ta JE.
Ina son Johnny English yana zuwa jirgi mai saukar ungulu sanye da rigar yaƙi ta zamanin da kuma harsashin rotor dinsa yana buga kwalkwali.
Kyautar Atkinson ga wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri yana kan allo, amma yanayin da ake ji da shi ya yi rauni sosai kuma ya zama mai ban mamaki, musamman tun lokacin da fina-finai masu ban mamaki kamar 007 da Mission Impossible kansu yanzu suna ba da kyauta a matsayin kayan aiki.
Ina jin kamar an yi wa yara dariya maimakon manya, kuma a wurina, rashin jin daɗin Johnny England ba shi da hankali kamar yadda Atkinson ya nuna a cikin mutumin Bean.
A halin yanzu, abin da ake ganin ya faru shi ne cewa Birtaniya na cikin matsala mai tsanani.
Wani dan jarida mai satar bayanai ya kutsa cikin gidan yanar gizo na 'yan leken asiri na Birtaniya, wanda ya gano sunayen duk wani dan sandan Birtaniya da ke wannan yankin, abin takaici ga dan sandan da ke aiki - wani dan kadan na Kevin Eldon.
