Masu ba ta shawara sun sanar da ita cewa idan an zargi kowane ɗan leƙen asiri, dole ne ta nemi wani mai ritaya.
Kuma wannan yana nufin cewa Johnny English da kansa, wanda ba shi da kwarewa, yana koyarwa a wani kyakkyawan wuri, amma yana ba da darussan da ba na hukuma ba game da yadda za a yi aiki a ɓoye: wasu kyawawan ban dariya a nan, tun da yake Turanci yana ba da makarantar makarantar Rock-style don leken asiri.
