A wannan Asabar, New York ce ke karbar bakuncin bikin Global Citizen Festival, wani biki na shekara-shekara na masu kida da ke da tarin taurari da ke nunawa da kuma wani aiki mai ban mamaki; kawo karshen talauci a duniya.
Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen zai ga dubun dubatan mutane sun taru a babban filin wasa na Central Park ba wai kawai don su ji dadin kallon Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mende ba, amma kuma don su kara wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin bikin, wato kawo karshen talauci a shekarar 2030.
Global Citizen Festival, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, fadada ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ta tallafi ta kasa da kasa da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke fama da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta zuwa taron (sai dai idan kuna son biyan tikitin VIP), masu halartar wasan kwaikwayon dole ne su kammala wasu ayyuka, ko ayyukan aikin sa kai; aika imel zuwa ga jagoran duniya, yin kiran waya ko wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don taimakawa wajen kara fahimtar manufar su na kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya Global Citizen ya kasance a cikin shekaru 12 da suka rage?
Shin ra'ayin bada kyauta ga jama'a da wasa kyauta hanya ce ta kwantar da hankalin jama'a su nemi kira zuwa aiki, ko kuwa wani misali ne na abin da ake kira clicktivism -- mutane suna jin cewa suna yin canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan kira ko aika tweet?
Tun daga shekarar 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta yi rajistar fiye da miliyan 19 na ayyukan da masu goyon bayanta suka yi, kuma ta shiga ciki da kuma matsa lamba kan wasu manufofi.
Ya ce wadannan ayyuka sun baiwa shugabannin duniya damar sanar da kudaden da suka kai fiye da dala biliyan 37, wanda zai shafi rayuwar mutane biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon shekarar 2018, kungiyar ta nuna alkawura da sanarwa 390 sakamakon hannun jarin su, daga cikinsu akalla dala biliyan 10 da aka riga aka biya ko aka tara.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa, tabbacin da aka samu ya shafi mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran su ne The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya ta masu zuba jari da 'yan kasuwa dake Birtaniya da ke da alhakin taimakawa yara su kai ga iyawarsu; ta yi alkawarin baiwa Rwanda dala miliyan 35 domin taimakawa wajen kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan ta karbi tweets sama da 4700 daga 'yan kasa da kasa.
 Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da tallafi, gwamnatocin kasa, da kuma 'yan kasa na duniya, kamar ku, za mu iya mayar da rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki zuwa takarda a tarihi  - jakadan The Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman, ta fadawa masu sauraro a wani taron raye a London a watan Afrilu na shekarar 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce bayan sun ɗauki fiye da ayyuka 5,000 don neman Ingilishi ya inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga uwaye da yara, gwamnatin Birtaniya ta sanar da kudade don wani shiri, The Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai mata da yara miliyan 5 ga maganin abinci mai gina jiki.
