Amurka na iya amfani da Sojan Ruwa a matsayin blockade don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - sakataren cikin gida
Washington na iya idan ya zama dole ta yi amfani da rundunar sojan ruwanta wajen hana makamashin Rasha kaiwa ga kasuwannin da suka hada da na Gabas ta Tsakiya, kamar yadda sakataren kasashen duniya Ryan Zinke ya bayyana, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa, shigar Rasha a Syria - musamman inda take aiki bisa gayyatar gwamnatin da ta dace - wata dama ce ta gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina tsammanin dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya, shi ne domin suna son su raba makamashi, kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai, kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma bisa ga jami'ai, akwai hanyoyin magance hakan.
"Amurka tana da wannan ikon, tare da rundunar sojan ruwanmu, na tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa a bude suke kuma, idan ya zama dole, ta toshe don tabbatar da cewa makamashin su ba ya zuwa kasuwa", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi magana ga mahalarta taron wanda aka shirya ta hanyar Ƙungiyar Energy Energy Alliance, wata ƙungiya mai mahimmanci da ke gabatar da kanta a matsayin muryar mai amfani da makamashi a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta hanyoyin da Washington ta bi wajen magance Rasha da Iran, kuma ya lura cewa sun yi kama.
"Hanyoyin tattalin arziki na Iran da Rasha sun fi ko kasa da amfani da kuma maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yayin da ya nuna Rasha a matsayin wani "farar-farar-farar-farar" da tattalin arziki ya dogara da man fetur.
Wannan sanarwa ta zo ne yayin da gwamnatin Trump ke kan aikin kara fitar da iskar gas mai narkewa zuwa Turai, don maye gurbin Rasha, wadda ita ce mafi arha ga masu amfani da Turai.
A wannan yanayin, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin samar da bututun mai mai suna Nord Stream 2, wanda a cewar Trump ya sanya Berlin a matsayin "kurkukun Moscow".
Moscow ta sha nanata cewa, aikin Nord Stream 2, wanda aka sa ran zai ninka karfin aikin da ake da shi zuwa biliyan 110 na murabba'in mita, aikin tattalin arziki ne.
Kreml ya yi ikirarin cewa, tsayayyar da Washington ke yi wa aikin ya samo asali ne kawai daga dalilai na tattalin arziki, kuma misali ne na rashin adalci.
"Ina ganin muna da ra'ayin cewa makamashi ba zai iya zama kayan aiki ba don matsa lamba kuma masu amfani su iya zaɓar masu samarwa", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Alexander Novak bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Har ila yau, Amurka ta janye koma baya daga Jamus, wanda ya tabbatar da alƙawarin da aka yi wa aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, Federation of German Industries (BDI), ta bukaci Amurka da ta kauce daga manufofin makamashi na EU da yarjejeniyar kasashen biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta uku ta katse mana samar da makamashi", inji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI) bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
