Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da cin zarafin mutane da tallace-tallace na farfaganda
Mako guda bayan wata jaridar kasar Sin ta fitar da wani tallan shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke nuna fa'idodin kasuwanci da Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba da ta gabata game da kudaden da jaridar China Daily ta biya a cikin kundin tarihin jihar Iowa - wanda shi ne babban kantin sayar da jaridu a jihar Iowa - bayan ya zargi kasar Sin da kokarin shiga cikin zaben Amurka a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da kasar Sin ta ki amincewa da shi.
Zargin Trump na cewa Beijing ta yi kokarin shiga cikin zaben Amurka, ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka fadawa Reuters wani sabon mataki ne a cikin wani yunkuri na Washington na matsa lamba kan China.
Yayin da al'ada ce ga kasashen waje su sanya talla don tallafawa kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin yakin kasuwanci mai girma wanda ya sa su ƙara haraji kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa.
An tsara farashin da kasar Sin ta yi a farkon yakin cinikayya don cin zarafin masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa da ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Trump ta Republican, in ji masana na kasar Sin da na Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
Kina, Branstad ya rubuta a wani ra'ayi a cikin ranar Lahadi Des Moines-register, yana ninka yanzu hargitsi ta hanyar gudanar da tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin 'yan jaridarmu.
"A cikin yada farfagandar, gwamnatin kasar Sin tana amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin faɗar albarkacin baki da kuma 'yancin latsawa ta hanyar sanya wani sanarwa da aka biya a cikin Registry na Des Moines", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin wannan, a kantin sayar da jaridu a gefen titi a nan Beijing, za ku sami muryoyin da suka bambanta da juna kuma ba za ku ga ainihin tunani na ra'ayoyi daban-daban da mutanen China za su iya yi ba game da matsalar tattalin arzikin kasar Sin, idan aka ba da cewa kafofin watsa labarai suna karkashin babban yatsan jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin".
Ya kara da cewa "daya daga cikin manyan jaridu na kasar Sin ta ki amincewa da tayin buga" labarinta, duk da cewa bai bayyana ko wace jarida ce ba.
