Tim Berners-Lee, mai kirkirar yanar gizo, ya kaddamar da wani kamfani da ke neman yin gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da kuma Google.
Aikin na ƙarshe na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ke gina Berners-Lees bude tushen tushen Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanai da kuma waɗanne mutane ke da damar zuwa wane irin bayani.
A cikin wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee yayi ba'a cewa ma'anar Inrupt shine domination.
