Doyle ita ce mafi kyawun wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo a Scotland, kuma shugaban kungiyar Ian Beattie ya bayyana taron a matsayin babbar dama ga wadanda ke jagorantar wasanni don amfani da kwarewarsu a matakin duniya a cikin shekaru goma da suka gabata.
