Girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da kuma tsunami da ya afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesiya a ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda jami'an gwamnati suka ce, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Ba tare da damar sadarwa ba, ma'aikatan agaji ba su samu wani bayani ba daga Donggala, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan da bala'in ya zama gaskiya.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, da ke tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ne, kuma yana a ƙarshen bakin teku mai nisan ruwa a gabar yammacin Sulawesi.
Birnin yana murnar cika shekaru 40 da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka afkawa birnin.
Donggala yanki ne wanda ya kai fiye da kilomita 300 a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin.
Yankin, wanda yanki ne na yanki mafi ƙasƙanci fiye da lardi, yana da yawan jama'a 299 200.
Kifi da kiwon daji sune abubuwan da ke cikin tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donggala.
Mahimmancin ma'adinan nickel a lardin, amma mafi yawanci an mayar da hankali ne a Morowali, a gefen Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar ofishin rage bala'i na Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938 an kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma an lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a lokacin tsunami a Donggala.
A shekarar 1996 yammacin Donggala ya fuskanci tsunami wanda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin kwararar girgizar kasa a cikin Tekun Fasihi kuma ana iya samun girgizar kasa.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar kasa da tsunami na shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai girma a yammacin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa kasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a bakin tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin wadannan a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar kasa mai girma ta afkawa yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Mutane dari da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 6.8 ta afka kudu da Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta haifar da tsunami da ya mamaye gabar teku ta kudu, inda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Yammacin Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1100 suka rasa rayukansu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 ta afkawa daya daga cikin tsibiran Mentawai a wajen Sumatra, inda ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata kauyuka da dama, ya kuma kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani karamin girgizar kasa ya afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya na Aceh, inda ya haifar da bala'i da kuma fargaba, inda aka tunatar da mutane da girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Babu tsunami da aka yi wannan lokacin, amma fiye da 100 sun rasa rayukansu a cikin gine-gine da suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok inda ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, mafi yawa a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar kasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido na wucin gadi a bakin teku.
