'Yan majalisar tarayya na son a yi wa wadanda ake zargi da aikata ta'addanci a New York hukuncin kisa
Jami'an tarayya a New York na son a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci wanda ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane takwas -- hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa ba saboda aikata laifi a jihar tun 1953.
An ce Saipov (30) ya yi amfani da motar haya daga Home Depot wajen kai hari kan hanyar hawa babur a kan hanyar West Side Highway a Manhattan a watan Oktoba, inda ya kori masu tafiya da kuma masu hawa babur a kan hanyar.
Don a iya tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, dole ne 'yan wasan kwaikwayo su iya tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda aka kashe da gangan kuma cewa ya da gangan ya yi wa wadanda suka yi mummunan rauni, a cewar wani bayanin da aka archived a kudancin gundumar New York.
Dukkanin wadannan abubuwan da suka faru na iya zama dalilin hukuncin kisa, in ji takardar shari'ar.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta ba da jerin sunayen 22 da aka zarge su, ciki har da zargin kisa guda takwas da aka yi da niyyar cin hanci da rashawa, wanda aka saba amfani da shi ta hanyar masu aikata laifuka na tarayya, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci ƙaddamarwa da kuma tsari, in ji 'yan wasan kwaikwayon kuma sun bayyana hanyar da Saipov ya kai harin a matsayin abin ƙyama, mummunan aiki da lalata.
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haddasa lalacewa da asarar dangi da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, an rubuta a cikin bayanin kula.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe su ne masu yawon bude ido daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a wani shari'a a yankin kudancin New York.
An yanke wa Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa na masu sayar da kayayyaki biyu, amma daga karshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumba na shekarar 2009.
A karo na karshe da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a cikin wani shari'ar tarayya a New York shine a 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin daurin rai saboda yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin yakin sanyi shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
A ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953, an kashe su duka a cikin wutar lantarki.
Saipov, asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin nunawa a cikin kwanaki da watanni da suka biyo baya, a cewar takardun shari'a.
Ya gaya wa 'yan sandan cewa abin da ya yi ya fi kyau.
Saipov ya shaidawa hukumomi cewa ya samu kwarin gwiwa wajen kai harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, kamar yadda takardar tuhumar ta nuna.
Ya kuma nemi a sanya tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya bayyana cewa bai yi laifi ba a duk wuraren da ake tuhumar sa.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare hakkin jama'a na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun yi matukar takaici da shawarar da mai gabatar da kara ya yanke.
"Muna ganin cewa yanke shawarar da aka yanke na neman hukuncin kisa, maimakon karbar hukuncin da ya ce mutum ya yi laifi da kuma zaman gidan yari na tsawon rai ba tare da damar sake shi ba, zai kara tsawaita raunin da ya faru ga duk wanda abin ya shafa", in ji Patton.
Masu kare Saipov sun riga sun nemi 'yan wasan da kada su yi kisa.
