Ta yaya yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya zama mai kyau ga Beijing
Tashin hankalin da ake samu a yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China ya yi kama da na bakin kunne, kuma yayin da yakin ya ci gaba, wani rikici tsakanin kasashen biyu na iya zama wata fa'ida ga Beijing a dogon lokaci, in ji masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya fara harbi a wannan shekara tare da yin haraji kan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa, ciki har da man fetur, karfe da kuma aluminum.
Ya yi tashin gwauron zabi a wannan makon, tare da harajin kayayyaki da suka kai dala biliyan 200, wanda hakan ke nufin cewa rabin kayayyakin da ake shigowa daga China zuwa Amurka ana biyan haraji.
Beijing ta dauki fansa ta sanya haraji tsakanin kashi biyar zuwa goma bisa dari kan kayayyakin Amurka masu darajar dala biliyan 60.
China ta yi alkawarin mayar wa Amurka duk wani harbi da ta harba, kuma tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu mafi girma, mai yiwuwa ba zai fadi ba a wuri na farko.
Don a sa Washington ta daina, dole ne China ta yi biyayya ga Amurka, amma yin biyayya ga Amurka abin kunya ne ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Duk da haka, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi shiru, matsin lamba na Amurka na iya yin tasiri mai kyau a kan tattalin arzikin China a cikin dogon lokaci, ta hanyar rage dogaro tsakanin tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa wani mataki na siyasa mai sauri a Washington ko Beijing zai iya sa tattalin arzikin kasashen biyu su fadi ya fi hatsari fiye da yadda mutane suka yi ta yarda da shi a baya", in ji Abigail Grace, mai bincike kan Asiya a Cibiyar Tsaro ta Amurka, mai tunani.
Syria a shirye don dawowar 'yan gudun hijira, in ji ministan harkokin wajen
Syria ta ce a shirye take ta karbi 'yan gudun hijira da suka dawo da kansu, kuma tana neman taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta lalace bayan yaki na shekaru bakwai.
A lokacin da yake jawabi a babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, ministan harkokin wajen kasar Walid al-Moualem ya ce halin da kasar ke ciki na samun ci gaba.
"Yau halin da ake ciki a kasa ya fi karko da tsaro, godiya ga ci gaban da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyara wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata domin dawo da yankunan da suka dace.
Dukkanin shirye-shirye sun kasance a yanzu don 'yan gudun hijira su iya komawa da yardar kansu zuwa ƙasar da suka yi tafiya a cikin ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki guda ɗaya wanda ya wuce rayuwar yau da kullum da kuma rayuwa.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da 'yan Syria miliyan 5.5 ne suka tsere daga kasar tun bayan yakin da aka yi a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida a kasar suna bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria tana son ta karbi tallafi don sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Amma ya jaddada cewa ba za su yarda da taimako ko taimako ba a kan wasu sharuɗɗa daga ƙasashen da ke tallafawa tawaye.
Turai ta samu nasara a gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup 2018 lokacin da ta doke tawagar Amurka da ci 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a Paris a Faransa.
Yanzu Amurka ta yi rashin nasara a Turai sau shida a jere, kuma ba ta lashe kofin Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta dawo da kambin a cikin tawagar dan kasar Denmark Thomas Bjørn, inda suka kai maki 14.5 da suke bukata domin doke Amurka.
