Sabuntawa akan dinoflagellate: An rage yawan taro a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da aka fitar kwanan nan daga hukumar kula da kifi da dabbobi ta Florida (FWC) ya nuna raguwar yawan dinosaur a yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, an ba da rahoton yanayin rashin daidaituwa ga ci gaban a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma jihohin da ke kewaye da Collier - wanda ke nuna raguwar yawan taro.
Ci gaban dinoflagellate ya bazu a kan kusan kilomita 200 a kan iyakar teku daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin lardin Lee.
Akwai yankunan da ke da dinoflagellate kimanin kilomita 16 a waje da gabar teku a Hillsborough, amma idan aka kwatanta da makon da ya gabata akwai yankuna da yawa.
An lura da Dinoflagellate a Pasco.
An ruwaito matsakaicin taro a Pinellas a makon da ya gabata, ƙananan zuwa babban taro a gabar tekun Hillsborough, ƙananan taro a Manatee, babban taro a gabar tekun Sarasota, matsakaicin taro a Charlotte, babban taro a Lee da ƙananan taro a Collier.
Har yanzu ana samun iritaccen yanayin a cikin hanyoyin iska a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Ba a ba da rahoton damuwa a cikin hanyoyin iska a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
